Content: @Markus KMDLabs is a coin we're launching that will incentivize testing various cryptoconditions and dapps. We'll be the first coin to use the MoMoM fungible chain scaling tech.

Content: Right now we're prepping for launch. We've been in development for about 9 months. There isn't much to be done at the moment, but after launch, we will have some dapps and CCs available to test. Right now if you're interested in developing a CC or dapp, we can help you along the way

Author: Alright#0419
Content: even if it's the simplest dapp you can think of, everyone has to start somewhere
